Mobile Phone & Camera Retail Sales Executive
Confidential Company - ,
Date Posted: 2014/04/29 13:12:57
Ref. JB3045484
Job Description
You will give technical advice or details or specifications to Online Customers on Mobile Phone, Camera and Laptop products and technologies.
You will enable customers to setup their devices for the first time and give quick tips and tricks to help them manage their devices. In addition, you will be responsible for driving incremental revenue by selling supplementary hardware and software products/services and ensure customers buy complete Hardware/ Software and accessories rather than individual products from the store.
You will also resolve customer technical issues and when required, assign Service Requests to the best-possible resources to ensure fast resolution and work closely with technical support team, to ensure that the upgrade requests have the appropriate level of priority, and are closed to the customer's satisfaction in a timely manner.
Skills
You should have good knowledge and experience in usage of Smart phones, tablets and Cameras. Graduation or Diploma.
You should have strong customer-service orientation and a minimum of 2 years of experience directly supporting end-customers. Additional sales/consultant experience will be a plus.
You are a passionate follower of global technology market and always up-to-date with the latest trends in personal computing and mobile gadgets, software services and applications.
You have a clear accent and able to talk with international customers (mostly UK / US)
This job is posted in the following Specialties:
